      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解为这是一个RR调度场景。需要几个进程？以及I/O操作也要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4",
        "p1 io",
        "p2 io",
        "p4 io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "四个进程P1到P4，都需要体现。P1、P2、P4有I/O操作，P3是纯计算。标题就叫\"Planificación Round Robin (Q=3) - Parte 1 (0-15s)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4",
        "p1 io",
        "p2 io",
        "p4 io",
        "0 15s",
        "q=3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先创建两个section：CPU和I/O。CPU部分开始画P1的第一个时间片，从0到3秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CPU",
        "P1(0-3)",
        "0 3",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，P1先运行3秒。然后P2从3秒开始，也是3秒时间片，到6秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2(3-6)",
        "3 6",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P2画好了。接下来P3从6到9？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3(6-9)",
        "6 9",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，P3用完时间片刚好结束，没有剩余时间。然后P4从9秒开始，但它只需要2秒就能完成，所以是9到11。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4(9-11)",
        "9 11",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P4画好了，标注到11秒。现在第一轮结束了，P1有剩余时间，要画P1的第二个时间片？",
